snippet.title: Space for Sale | Showcase 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
Space for Sale is now in Early Access! Go solo or share the exciting space realtor journey with a friend and double your chances of success in two player co-op. Venture out in your trusty ship to discover the wonders of the solar system!

- Links & Info - 
Steam: https://thqn.net/sfs-steam
Website: https://spaceforsale.thqnordic.com 
Discord: https://discord.gg/Fu9cxydQ4j
